        "subject": "LU-0000 tests: remove standalone lease test scripts",
        "message": "LU-0000 tests: remove standalone lease test scripts\n\nRemove standalone test scripts in favor of integrated tests\nin sanity-flr.sh. All immediate mirror lease functionality\ntests are now properly integrated into the existing test\nframework as tests 213a through 213f.\n\nThe standalone scripts were redundant since the functionality\nis already covered by the integrated tests which follow\nthe standard Lustre testing patterns and can be run with\nthe auster framework.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ic4fc377dc1415aa72d7a76e56d4ce7378fd2f964\n"
